Summary of reviews<br />=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D<br=
 /><br />Thank you for your work on extending AgentSpeak (L) to better mana=
ge goal reasoning. The reviewers agree that the work is interesting. Howeve=
r, as can be seen from their reviews, they all have concerns with the work =
presented. The main criticism is around the evaluation. Although the paper =
claims this extension improves four aspects as mentioned in the introductio=
n, there is no empirical evidence that it does. This is something the autho=
rs should address to improve upon this work. The reviewers have also made o=
ther useful suggestions which I hope the authors will take onboard.









